on and the second accounts for\nsystematics both in the measurements and in the model. For the full sample,\n$z=0.15-0.47$, we find $H(z=0.34)= 83.80 \\pm 2.96 (\\pm 1.59)$ km/s/Mpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2008 19:45:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jul 2008 15:52:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 25 Jul 2008 07:31:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 22 May 2009 19:01:32 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2009 17:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
