ations of dust formation in SNe are sparse, so these results\nprovide a rare opportunity to consider SNe Type IIn as dust sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2008 19:45:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Dec 2008 21:04:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
